  "source_question": "The source paper recalls Kalton's question whether Lipschitz free spaces over separable uniformly discrete metric spaces have the bounded approximation property. It notes that it suffices to consider nets N in Banach spaces X, that the case where X has separable dual is positive, and that the case of a general separable Banach space X remains open.",
